CHIPS ACTUAL CHIPS NOT FRIES BUT CHIPS. SOGGY SALTY CHUNKY GLORIOUS CHIPS. DONT GET ME STARTED ON THE SAUSAGES, THEY ARE GOD TIER SAUSAGES.
Exquisite pies!

I had followed Stargazy on instagram and have wanted to try it for years. Tonight my husband and I treated ourselves to take out and chose Stargazy's Sunday roast. This meal was HEAVEN ON A PLATE. They give perfect reheat instructions. …
One of the best places to eat in Philly! Have tried almost everything on the menu and would recommend all of it!
These guys are the best! We’ve had the pies before and they are delicious. Went in tonight for fish and chips and they were amazing right down to the mushy peas. Best in Philly!!!

Awesome little spot on passyunk. First time go simple one pie one mash with the liquor and grab a clanger too. Then dive into all the different varieties they have and rotate through. Big Tottenham guy too, Come on you Spurs!

Would highly recommend this to anyone who’s in the East Passyunk area. These guys are always so nice to us and their food never disappoints. My go-to is the cheese and onion pasty but everything else I’ve had has been great.

Serious comfort food! Had a bunch of different pies from here and they all are HITTING. You can't go wrong. I knew the brits were masters at cynicism, now I know they have savory pies on the resume as well. Order anything on the menu and Enjoy.
The best ever, at everything.

Especially because the pie was plopped out of the pie tin straight into an open palm and into our plates. Our experience would have been perfect otherwise. Will come back!
